	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64534021">It's not just a piece of paper, getting a license involves hiring the right (safety)people who have the right licensed and implementing safetymeasures. In this case it would have required at least one ambulance, a firetruck and a pilot who is licensed to have pyrotechnics on board his aircraft. It would also require a stunt coordinator to make sure the whole thing was planned with plans for what to do in an emergency.</div>
	</div>

